      "writtenOn": "2016-08-03T17:06:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thanks for explaining this.  My own inclination would be to put this explanation in the code -- but I have a maybe tend to value detailed explanations like this in the code more than some, and reasonable people can differ.  I leave it up to you; maybe some shortened form of this?  Maybe mentioning the point that if the timeout happens, other errors will be triggered is worth mentioning.",
